<section id="hero" class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
  <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-site-heading tracking-tight mb-4">
    Brad Duhon
  </h1>
  <p class="text-xl text-amber-dark font-medium italic mb-6">
    Least privilege. Maximum curiosity.
  </p>
  <p class="text-site-text max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
    Curious by nature, paranoid by profession. I'm drawn to the security problems
    that don't have a checkbox - where you have to understand the system deeply
    before you can reason about what could go wrong. I build controls, chase edge
    cases, and document the gotchas so the next person doesn't hit the same wall.
    I write things down so future me doesn't have to figure them out twice.
    That's mostly what this site is.
  </p>
</section>
